SUMMARY:We by Yevgeny Zamyatin
DESCRIPTION:Post-Apocalyptic Book Club - Toronto Chapter\nOur next book will be We by Yevgeny Zamyatin. Here's the blurb:\n\nThe exhilarating dystopian novel that inspired George Orwell's 1984 and foreshadowed the worst excesses of Soviet Russia.\n\nYevgeny Zamyatin's *We* is a powerfully inventive vision that has influenced writers from George Orwell to Ayn Rand. In a glass-enclosed city of absolute straight lines\, ruled over by the all-powerful 'Benefactor'\, the citizens of the totalitarian society of OneState live out lives devoid of passion and creativity - until D-503\, a mathematician who dreams in numbers\, makes a discovery: he has an individual soul. Set in the twenty-sixth century AD\, *We* is the classic dystopian novel and was the forerunner of works such as George Orwell's *1984* and Aldous Huxley's *Brave New World*. It was suppressed for many years in Russia and remains a resounding cry for individual freedom\, yet is also a powerful\, exciting and vivid work of science fiction.\n\nNote for this book - there are a large variety of versions and translations!\nThe book is available here:\n\nAmazon- Paperback\, eBook\, Audiobook:\nhttps://www.amazon.ca/We-New-Yevgeny-Zamyatin/dp/0140185852/ref=sr_1_1?crid=1F40XUYQSJJR5&dib=eyJ2IjoiMSJ9.qtnfVTNJy7sDsVS0eoa9JtqB7JoGb8sAn0aoNr9Rfsc_cy-44iL7-uNztrGRAAfSgc0OOyZps2gind9jIK192fuDkP9C1GW0p-5icZpnVnkHroJKALac03KjwgbNFxRnm4GDhyEC0wJLjwhJVB7mfXJ_a0f2J7mXdKMiN7OznwQpOmxma-hl5BnUIj3BYMxPzpolK8-0otroPxbpgWlImLccJvVam7IlIjSavo_UJ3I.keBYwutgNiLNXMPGPfa2gwaQU_j60nv4Iou9lWThOXE&dib_tag=se&keywords=we+zamyatin&qid=1768345285&s=books&sprefix=we+zamyatin%2Cstripbooks%2C105&sr=1-1\n\nIndigo- Paperback:\nhttps://www.indigo.ca/en-ca/we-a-novel/9780771050220.html\n\nKobo- eBook:\nhttps://www.kobo.com/ca/en/ebook/we-2?sId=c05b9047-f00c-4d46-99ec-a975db6170b2&ssId=BBrkaNNgMIF1oXV-VzSs8&cPos=19\n\nToronto Public Library:\nhttps://www.torontopubliclibrary.ca/detail.jsp?Entt=RDM530463&R=530463\n\nToronto Public Library- eBook https://toronto.overdrive.com/media/971F3D86-F246-4CB9-A3CB-94738696A77C\n\nProject Gutenberg:\nhttps://www.gutenberg.org/ebooks/61963
